{"tid":1276793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣智取] 警員可抗不合法命令 612 暴政鎮壓市民 71 空城不設防換政治籌碼","createTime":"2019-07-02T04:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:09:28.000Z","uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa78676b0697acc5cb683921379ae733e76a0e9","tid":1276793,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警員可抗不合法命令</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">612 暴政鎮壓市民 用過份武力 開槍鎮壓 <br />\n71 空城不設防換政治籌碼 故意放水 不保護立法會</span><br />\n</span></strong>[/quote]</div><br />\n<br />\n本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言（或，謹向全能之主發誓），本人會竭誠依法為香港特別行政區政府效力為警務人員，遵從、支持及<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">維護香港特別行政區的法律</span></strong>，以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠、努力的態度</strong></span>行使職權，執行職務，並且毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一切合法命令</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=360178674734219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D360178674734219&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=578dccd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=360178674734219</a><br />\n<br />\n警務人員<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律</span></strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">(不是香港特別行政區特首及一哥)</span><br />\n依家佢地香港警察以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">徇私</span></strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">(幫政府)</span>、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對他人</span></strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">(市民或黃絲)</span><span style=\"color: red;\">懷惡意、敵視他人</span>[/b]<span style=\"color: gold;\">(市民或黃絲)</span>的態度行使職權<br />\n毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一切違法命令</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">警隊抱負、目標及價值觀</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/01_about_us/vm.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F01_about_us%2Fvm.html&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=7ad7da23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/01_about_us/vm.html</a><br />\n剩係以612同71計<br />\n目標: <br />\n為確保社會安穩，<strong>香港警隊</strong>務必：<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n- 維護法紀 (71無做到) <br />\n- <strong>維持治安</strong> (71無做到)<br />\n- <strong>防止</strong>及偵破罪案 (71無做到)<br />\n- <strong>保障市民生命財產</strong> (612及71冇做到)<br />\n- <strong>與市民大眾及其他機構維持緊密合作和聯繫</strong> (612及 71冇做到)<br />\n- 凡事悉力以赴，力求做得最好  (612及 71冇做到)<br />\n- <strong>維持市民對警隊的信心</strong> (612及 71冇做到)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家香港警隊做到以上邊一項?"},{"pid":"bce3e32d433222714c672b73efff9844b95e241f","tid":1276793,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfabf62030b00980e1cffa3a199623b9c92e863d","tid":1276793,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:55:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c314de760e983bc078c1579f37922da436394773","tid":1276793,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"《文宣組。宣傳易》細緻分工 善用Airdrop<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276727\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276727</a><br />\n<br />\n【文宣組回合、鍵盤戰士集合】入嚟拎文宣材料整合，一齊打贏輿論戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275914\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275914</a><br />\n<br />\n［文宣智取］輿論戰核彈 政府警察故意引示威者入立法會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dddqNS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dddqNS</a><br />\n<br />\n[文智] 武力相對論 學生只是手推車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dcEtiS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dcEtiS</a><br />\n<br />\n【 學下官腔】如何應對短期内排山倒海的「嚴厲譴責示威人士使用暴力」？ 給香港的七點回應<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1274862\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1274862</a><br />\n<br />\n【 突發】《香港己亥宣言》中英日三語登場！盡力為香港定下重光藍圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276561\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276561</a><br />\n<br />\n［文宣組入嚟］輿論戰材料集合！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275652\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275652</a><br />\n<br />\n[文宣/請廣傳]回應特首林鄭月娥記者會聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1275646\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1275646</a>"},{"pid":"67c93b6c0ead9998480bb0ea0e4def35f4d9ac36","tid":1276793,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7032695a4e6921871edd2f8b07ee4cd6d06b9e","tid":1276793,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"克警英姿：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F450867315005279%2Fposts%2F2299277576830901%2F&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=6f7aecb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901/</a><br />\n<br />\n612嗰日一位16歲女學生嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建議大家可以聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完之後我好嬲，亦都好想喊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月12日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月1日<br />\n香港警察面對手無寸鐵既示威者亂棍打人，窮追猛打<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqbm0Uy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpqbm0Uy.gif&h=0d6106c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：（2019年6月12日）<br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=b5d4e713\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=f746deaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=b187d654\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=ca588cde\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=dc8d3e3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=87e4982d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a>"},{"pid":"033459f3b5970e591db6e3b321b93bfcf895da48","tid":1276793,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpL3vUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpL3vUL.jpg&h=26b79386&s